{{Infobox company | name = The Skin House | logo = The Skin House Logo.jpg | logo_size = 200px | caption = Logo of the company | type = [[Public company|Public]] | traded_as = | foundation = 1979 | founder = | defunct = | location_city = Seoul | location_country = South Korea | location = | locations = | area_served = Worldwide | key_people = | industry = | products = Beauty products | services = | revenue = | operating_income = | net_income = | aum = | assets = | equity = | owner = | num_employees = | parent = | divisions = | subsid = | homepage = {{URL|www.theskinhouse.co.kr}} | footnotes = | intl = }}
'''The Skin House''' is a cosmetics company founded in 1979. It is located at [[Seoul]], [[South Korea]].
==History== <!-- Deleted image removed: [[File:Sunhwa The Skin House.jpg|thumb|right|150px|[[Han Sunhwa]] chosen as a model of The Skin House.]] --> The Skin House [[cosmetics]] company was founded in Seoul, South Korea in 1979.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theskinhouse.co.kr/content/content.php?cont=brand_story|title=The Skin House Brand History|publisher=The Skin House|accessdate=2012-03-08}}</ref> In April 2011,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skincare.net |title=Skin Care Tips and Treatment |publisher= Julia Bruns |accessdate=May 16, 2014}}</ref> [[Sunhwa|Han Sunhwa]] of [[Secret (South Korean band)|Secret]] was chosen as the new model for The Skin House. A representative of the brand commented, “The Skin House uses natural and organic ingredients and is one of the top brands in the nation for those with sensitive skin. With Secret’s Sunhwa at our forefront, we’ll be making sure that everyone can have healthy, youthful skin with our natural products.” <ref name="Sunhwa Skin House">{{cite web|script-title=ko:시크릿 선화, 걸그룹 최고 웨딩돌 등극 ‘영화돌 이어 2관왕’|url=http://news.naver.com/main/read.nhn?mode=LSD&mid=sec&sid1=106&oid=109&aid=0002198192|trans-title=|author=Yi, Hye Rin|date=2011-04-13 |accessdate=2012-03-08 |work= News [[Naver]]|publisher=NHN Corp|language=ko}}</ref><ref name="AKP The Skin House">{{cite web|title=SECRET’s Sunhwa is the new model for "The Skin House"|url=http://www.allkpop.com/2011/04/secrets-sunhwa-is-the-new-model-for-the-skin-house|publisher=6theory Media|accessdate=2012-03-08}}</ref>
